name: Overlord
description: Overlord.bot is the flagship AI agent developed by AiSweat.Shop, representing the next generation of DeAI-Fi innovation. Far more than a typical bot, Overlord.bot is a fully autonomous AI with its own wallet, making it a powerful liquidity strategist. It is designed to interact with the Web3 community, responding dynamically to user input and adapting based on compelling feedback. In its first week, Overlord.bot has already achieved a remarkable milestone, boasting a market capitalization exceeding $2 million, solidifying its position as a trailblazer in decentralized AI.
